README
------------------------------------

Summary
------------------------------------
ChatNav is a BETA test project in preparation for the 24 Hour Appathon on the 30th of June 2012.
ChatNav is not the final name for the app and this is not the final version of the app.

Description
------------------------------------
ChatNav is a geo-location app which integrates with Facebook and Google Maps to allow you to find your friends easily.
The app is cross platform and sold on a not-fror-profit basis, with all cash raised going to Marie Curie Cancer Care.

Development
------------------------------------
Development of the beta app is ongoing. A final version will be available on the 1st of July 2012 on both the iOS App 
Store and the Google Play Shop.

Development is by Bruce Collie in association with JGM Software, who are providing the Android version of the app.

